  "translations": {
    "en": "And many an evil cloud You have dispersed, and many an overwhelming suffering You have relieved, You are not questioned about Your acts! But You were asked and You granted, and (even if) You were not asked, You initiated! And Your bounty was sought and You never turned it down. You have ordained nothing but good, while I have persisted in breaking through Your injunctions, trespassing the limits set by You and being heedless to Your warning! So all praise and thanks to You, O my Lord, the Mighty, Who cannot be overcome and, the Patient Who has no hurry. This indeed is the place for one to confess ones default, and to testify against oneself its ruination.",
